{
  "id": "adv_group_thrx_03_05",
  "title": "IIIX 03 05",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "press-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "host",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-host.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05-host001.m4a",
      "text": "えー、I-UNITYセミファイナルに向けまして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ for the I-UNITY semi-finals…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 4.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "host",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-host.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05-host002.m4a",
      "text": "ここからは、各グループの代表者に意気込みを\n伺っていきたいと思います。まずはmihoさんから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "From here on out‚ we would like to ask\neach group's representative about their aspirations. First‚ from miho-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.3,
      "endTime": 11.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "press-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "はい。私達スリクスとしては\nこのセミファイナルをとても楽しみにしていました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ as for us ⅢX‚\nwe were very much looking forward to these semi-finals.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.9333333333,
      "endTime": 18.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "月のテンペストの皆様のご活躍は聞きしに勝りますし\n同じ舞台に立てるのを誇りに感じてもいます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Moon Tempest’s activities are impressive as I had heard‚\nand I feel proud to be able to stand on the same stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.9333333333,
      "endTime": 26.4552609761,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "press-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "……ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Thank you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.6666666667,
      "endTime": 30.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "press-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "ただ個人的には、月のテンペストとしてではなく……\n長瀬琴乃さんと戦えるのが、楽しみでもあります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However‚ personally‚ not as Moon Tempest…\nI am also looking forward to being able to fight Kotono Nagase-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.5666666667,
      "endTime": 38.8973015467,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "press-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "私、こう見えて麻奈さんの大ファンなので……\nその妹さんと戦えるなんて、夢のようだな、と",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You see‚ I’m actually a big fan of Mana-san…\nSo to be able to fight her sister is like a dream come true.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.1,
      "endTime": 47.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "press-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "press-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "（あら、あちらでマネージャーが妙な顔をしているわ）\n（……心外ね、嘘は言っていないわよ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Oh my‚ our manager-san is making a strange face over there.）\n（…How rude‚ I wasn’t lying.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.0333333333,
      "endTime": 56.2556304961,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "press-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "（誰より長瀬麻奈のことを考えているのは私だもの）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I'm the one who thinks about Mana Nagase more than anyone else.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.4666666667,
      "endTime": 60.602698342,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "press-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "私達も、アイドルシーンを代表するスリクスと\n同じ舞台に立てるのを、光栄に感じています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We are also honored to be able to stand on the\nsame stage with ⅢX‚ who represent the idol scene.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.8,
      "endTime": 67.53333333329999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "press-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "ですから――\nスリクスのみなさんも、正々堂々臨んで下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That is why――\nⅢX‚ please face us fair and square.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.7666666667,
      "endTime": 72.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "press-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "……ええ、もちろんです\nセミファイナル、一緒に盛り上げていきましょうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes‚ of course.\nLet’s liven up the semi-finals together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.9,
      "endTime": 79.28974734100001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――I-UNITYセミファイナル当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――It's the day of the I-UNITY semi-finals.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.4,
      "endTime": 83.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.3248682658
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.3248682658
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "krk",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kiriko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05-krk001.m4a",
      "text": "三人とも、三時にはステージで最終確認が始まるわ\nそれまでに準備は終わらせてね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The three of you‚ the final check on stage will start at three o’clock.\nPlease finish preparing by then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.4,
      "endTime": 91.89401116580001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "はい、分かりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I understand.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.1,
      "endTime": 94.1666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "……ちっ、敏腕気取りで偉そ～に\n小細工なしでもこっちは十分勝てるっての",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Tch‚ acting all competent and high and mighty.\nAs if we can’t win easily even without her tricks.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.6,
      "endTime": 101.9237648179,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ほらあそこ、星見プロの子達ももう来てる\nでも、なんか凄い周りを気にしてるね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ look over there‚ the kids from Hoshimi Production are already here.\nBut it looks like they’re really conscious of their surroundings.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.6,
      "endTime": 113.1076922197,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃあ、この間スキャンダルが出たばかりだもの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well yeah‚ a scandal just came out about them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.3,
      "endTime": 117.0946484566,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "マネージャーとの不適切な関係に、労基法無視ねえ……\n労基法無視だけは心の底から同情するけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "An inappropriate relationship with their manager‚ ignoring labor laws…\nI sympathize with the labor laws part from the bottom of my heart‚ though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.3,
      "endTime": 127.1611232858,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "……そうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That’s true.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.3666666667,
      "endTime": 128.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "（十中八九、姫野さんの手配なのでしょうけど……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Nine times out of ten‚ Himeno-san is behind this‚ isn’t she…?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.1666666667,
      "endTime": 133.3546485583,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "krk",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kiriko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05-krk002.m4a",
      "text": "まさか、美帆子まであの子達に同情しているの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you serious? Even Mihoko-san sympathizes with those kids?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.5666666667,
      "endTime": 137.2333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "それこそ「まさか」ですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s absurd.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.4333333333,
      "endTime": 139.6109070619,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 139.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_03_05-kor004.m4a",
